&quot;I want to become cute for that guy that I like, but... Honestly, I'm not very fashionable. However, I truly want to become prettier, so I am trying my best to fix up my hair and dressing style. But despite all my efforts, nothing is going right, and my childhood friend, Koudai, keeps treating me like a child! How can I make him say that I'm cute...?&quot;

The other story is a oneshot Daydream World:
Kubo is a girl who lives in her own little daydream world, where people are destined to be together, and Ferris Wheels exist for couples bound by eternal love. That world is turned upside down when the boy she likes starts working with her at her part-time job. Is it time for Kubo to wake up from her daydreams and face reality?
